Class JungJGraphModelAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.undo.UndoableEditSupport
      • org.jgraph.graph.DefaultGraphModel
        • org.apache.oodt.cas.workflow.gui.perspective.view.impl.JungJGraphModelAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.jgraph.graph.GraphModel

    public class JungJGraphModelAdapter
extends org.jgraph.graph.DefaultGraphModel
    This class integrates OODT, Jung and JGraph. Not necessarily in that order. It acts as a facade, wrapping a Jung graph (and its modifications) and then using that to update the current state of the associated JGraph model.
    Author:
    mattmann
